  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3722070/extras/8bacc47451c392ebdb2c4ef5f2189bc9.avif?t=1748316855\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3722070/extras_big/8bacc47451c392ebdb2c4ef5f2189bc9.avif?t=1748316855 width=800 height=532 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’ve just been hired as the new night security guard at this massive mart.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your task is simple, walk the halls, check the offices, the store floor, and the warehouse, and activate all patrol panels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whatever else happens during your shift… is not the company’s concern.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3722070/extras/4f08c851be7094851d9ff2ae0fe9c697.poster.avif?t=1748316855\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3722070/extras/4f08c851be7094851d9ff2ae0fe9c697.webm?t=1748316855\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3722070/extras/4f08c851be7094851d9ff2ae0fe9c697.mp4?t=1748316855\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You must patrol the mart as instructed by the company.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Patrol panels are located in the office, the store area, and the warehouse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Activate all of these panels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once every panel is activated, your daily duty is complete.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3722070/extras/03448bdd4a00172831b2d3a1d3bbe3b8.avif?t=1748316855\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3722070/extras_big/03448bdd4a00172831b2d3a1d3bbe3b8.avif?t=1748316855 width=800 height=800 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete the pentagram panels in the abandoned mart in the normal, inverted, or random order to experience multiple endings.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3722070/extras/8bacc47451c392ebdb2c4ef5f2189bc9.avif?t=1748316855\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3722070/extras_big/8bacc47451c392ebdb2c4ef5f2189bc9.avif?t=1748316855 width=800 height=532 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’ve just been hired as the new night security guard at this massive mart.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your task is simple, walk the halls, check the offices, the store floor, and the warehouse, and activate all patrol panels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whatever else happens during your shift… is not the company’s concern.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3722070/extras/4f08c851be7094851d9ff2ae0fe9c697.poster.avif?t=1748316855\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3722070/extras/4f08c851be7094851d9ff2ae0fe9c697.webm?t=1748316855\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3722070/extras/4f08c851be7094851d9ff2ae0fe9c697.mp4?t=1748316855\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You must patrol the mart as instructed by the company.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Patrol panels are located in the office, the store area, and the warehouse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Activate all of these panels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once every panel is activated, your daily duty is complete.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3722070/extras/03448bdd4a00172831b2d3a1d3bbe3b8.avif?t=1748316855\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3722070/extras_big/03448bdd4a00172831b2d3a1d3bbe3b8.avif?t=1748316855 width=800 height=800 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete the pentagram panels in the abandoned mart in the normal, inverted, or random order to experience multiple endings.</p>",
